Class MappedIntProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.properties.AbstractInventoryProperty<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Integer>
      • org.spongepowered.api.item.inventory.properties.MappedIntProperty
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<InventoryProperty<?,?>>, InventoryProperty<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Integer>

    public class MappedIntProperty
extends AbstractInventoryProperty<java.lang.Integer,java.lang.Integer>
    An integer-mapped integer property. This is primarily used for supporting the "fields" on the beacon inventory for the moment. This property is also settable.
